column2: SELECT TOP #  s.plate,s.mjd,s.fiberid,p.run,p.rerun,p.camCol,p.field,p.obj  FROM ..SpecObj as s  JOIN ..PhotoObj AS p ON s.bestObjID = p.objID  JOIN dbo.fGetObjFromRect(#,#,#,#) AS b ON s.bestobjid = b.objID  WHERE s.zWarning = # AND (s.primTarget & (dbo.fPrimTarget(&&&) + dbo.fPrimTarget(&&&) + dbo.fPrimTarget(&&&) + dbo.fPrimTarget(&&&) + dbo.fPrimTarget(&&&) + dbo.fPrimTarget(&&&) + dbo.fPrimTarget(&&&) + dbo.fPrimTarget(&&&) + dbo.fPrimTarget(&&&) + dbo.fPrimTarget(&&&)) > #)
